@model Marofh.Models.RegisterViewModel
@using Resources
@{

    var culture = System.Threading.Thread.CurrentThread.CurrentUICulture.Name.ToLowerInvariant();
    if (culture.Contains("en-us"))
    {
          ViewBag.Title = "Create New Account";
    }
    else
    {

          ViewBag.Title = "انشاء مستخدم جديد";
    }



}

@{
  
    ViewBag.Parent = "المستخدمين";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_LayoutInner.cshtml";

}



@using (Html.BeginForm("Register", "Kafil", FormMethod.Post, new { @class = "form-horizontal", role = "form" }))
{
    @Html.AntiForgeryToken()

    <section>

        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="wizard-content-1 pos-flex clearfix">
                <div class="steps d-inline-block clearfix">
                    <span class="bg-shape"></span>
                    <ul class="tablist multisteps-form__progress">
                        <li class="multisteps-form__progress-btn">
                            <div class="step-btn-icon-text">
                                <span>1</span>
                                <div class="step-btn-icon float-right position-relative">
                                    <i class="fal fa-user-circle iconifo"></i>

                                </div>
                                <div class="step-btn-text">
                                    <h2 class="text-uppercase">@*نوع الحساب*@ @Resource.AccountType</h2>
                                    <span class="text-capitalize"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="multisteps-form__progress-btn js-active current">
                            <div class="step-btn-icon-text">
                                <span>2</span>
                                <div class="step-btn-icon float-right position-relative">


                                    <i class="fal fa-address-card iconifo"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step-btn-text">
                                    <h2 class="text-uppercase">@*استكمال البيانات*@  @Resource.CompletingData</h2>
                                    <span class="text-capitalize"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="multisteps-form__progress-btn">
                            <div class="step-btn-icon-text">
                                <span>3</span>
                                <div class="step-btn-icon float-right position-relative">

                                    <i class="far fa-check-circle iconifo"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step-btn-text">
                                    <h2 class="text-uppercase">@*تم التسجيل*@  @Resource.RegistrationIsDone </h2>
                                    <span class="text-capitalize"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="step-inner-content clearfix position-relative">
                    <span class="bg-shape"></span>
                    <div class="multisteps-form__form" id="wizard">
                        <div class="form-area position-relative">
                            <div class="multisteps-form__panel" data-animation="scaleIn">
                                <div class="wizard-forms position-relative">
                                    <span class="step-no position-absolute"> @Resource.FirstStep  </span>
                                    <div class="wizard-progress">
                                        <span> @*مرحلة 1 من 3*@   @Resource.Stage1of3</span>
                                        <div class="progress">
                                            <div class="progress-bar">
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="wizard-inner-box">
                                        <div class="inner-title text-center mb-50">
                                            <h2> @Resource.SelectAccountType   </h2>
                                            <p> @Resource.ChooseTypeofAccountyouWanttoOpen</p>
                                        </div>



                                        <div class="acounttyupe text-center">



                                            <label class="need-job-icon-text text-center">
                                                <input type="radio" name="job_title" value="Ux designer label" class="j-checkbox">
                                                <span class="need-job-text-inner">
                                                    <span class="checkbox-circle-mark position-absolute"> </span>
                                                    <span class="need-job-icon">
                                                        <img src="/Content/front/assets/img/imagenew/n.jpg" />
                                                    </span>
                                                    <span class="need-job-text">
                                                        <span class="text-uppercase need-job-title"> @Resource.BusinessOwner  عملspan>
                                                    </span>
                                                </span>
                                            </label>
                                            <label class="need-job-icon-text text-center">
                                                <input type="radio" name="job_title" value="Front Developer" class="j-checkbox">
                                                <span class="need-job-text-inner">
                                                    <span class="checkbox-circle-mark position-absolute"> </span>
                                                    <span class="need-job-icon">

                                                        <img src="/Content/front/assets/img/imagenew/office.jpg" />
                                                    </span>
                                                    <span class="need-job-text">
                                                        <span class="text-uppercase need-job-title">@Resource.RecruitingOffice  </span>
                                                    </span>
                                                </span>
                                            </label>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="actions">
                                        <ul>
                                            <li><span class="js-btn-next" title="NEXT"> @Resource.Next </span></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bottom-vector position-absolute">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- step 1 -->
                            <div class="multisteps-form__panel  js-active" data-animation="scaleIn">
                                <div class="wizard-forms form-step-2">
                                    <span class="step-no position-absolute">  @Resource.SecondStep</span>
                                    <div class="wizard-progress">
                                        <span>  @Resource.Stage2of3</span>
                                        <div class="progress">
                                            <div class="progress-bar" style="width: 66%;">
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="wizard-inner-box ">
                                        <div class="inner-title text-center">
                                            <h2>  @Resource.BusinessOwner</h2>
                                            <p>  @Resource.CompleteYourAccountInformation  </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="container ">
                                        <div class="radio-tile-group">

                                            <div class="input-container">
                                                <input id="male" class="radio-button" type="radio" name="gender" />
                                                <div class="radio-tile">
                                                    <div class="icon">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-male"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <label for="male" class="radio-tile-label"> @Resource.Male</label>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="input-container">
                                                <input id="female" class="radio-button" type="radio" name="gender" />
                                                <div class="radio-tile">
                                                    <div class="icon">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-female"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <label for="female" class="radio-tile-label"> @Resource.Female </label>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="details-form-area">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                                <div class="form-input-inner position-relative has-float-label">
                                                    <input type="text" name="FName" id="FName" placeholder="@Resource.FirstName" class="form-control" required>
                                                    <label>@Resource.FirstName   </label>
                                                    <div class="icon-bg text-center">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                                                    </div>

                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                                <div class="form-input-inner position-relative has-float-label">
                                                    <input type="text" name="LName" id="LName" placeholder="@Resource.LastName" class="form-control">
                                                    <label> @Resource.LastName</label>
                                                    <div class="icon-bg text-center">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                                                    </div>

                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                                <div class="form-input-inner position-relative has-float-label">
                                                    <input type="email" name="Email" id="Email" placeholder="@Resource.Email " class="form-control" required>
                                                    <label>   @Resource.Email</label>
                                                    <div class="icon-bg text-center">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                                <div class="form-input-inner position-relative has-float-label">
                                                    <input type="number" pattern="/^-?\d+\.?\d*$/" onKeyPress="if(this.value.length==10) return false;" style="text-align: right; margin-right: 25px;" id="Mobile" name="Mobile" placeholder="@Resource.PhoneNumber" class="form-control">
                                                    <!--<label>رقم الهاتف</label>-->
                                                    <div class="icon-bg text-center">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                                <div class="form-input-inner select-option-area position-relative">
                                                    @Html.DropDownList("CountryID", ViewBag.CountryID as List<SelectListItem>, Resource.Country, htmlAttributes: new { required = "required", oninvalid = "this.setCustomValidity(' الدولة ')", oninput = "setCustomValidity('')", @class = "form-control", @onfocus = "this.size = 10; this.width = 100%; ", @onblur = "this.size = 1; ", @onchange = "this.size = 1; this.blur();   " })

                                                    <div class="icon-bg text-center">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-flag-checkered"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                                <div class="form-input-inner select-option-area position-relative">
                                                    @Html.DropDownList("CityID", ViewBag.CityID as List<SelectListItem>, Resource.ChooseCity, htmlAttributes: new { required = "required", oninvalid = "this.setCustomValidity(' المدينة ')", oninput = "setCustomValidity('')", @class = "form-control", @onfocus = "this.size = 10; this.width = 100%; ", @onblur = "this.size = 1; ", @onchange = "this.size = 1; this.blur();" })

                                                    <div class="icon-bg text-center">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>


                                            <div class="input-filed-innerbox">
                                                <div class="row">
                                                    <div class="col-lg-12">
                                                        <div class="row">

                                                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                                                <div class="form-input-inner position-relative has-float-label">
                                                                    <span toggle="#password-field" class="fa fa-fw fa-eye field-icon toggle-password toggle-password2"></span>

                                                                    <input placeholder="@Resource.Password" id="Password" type="password" class="form-control" name="Password" required>
                                                                    <label>@Resource.Password </label>
                                                                    <div class="icon-bg text-center">
                                                                        <i class="fas fa-lock-alt"></i>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>


                                                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                                                <div class="form-input-inner position-relative has-float-label">
                                                                    <span toggle="#password-field2" class="fa fa-fw fa-eye field-icon toggle-password toggle-password3"></span>

                                                                    <input placeholder="@Resource.Password" id="ConfirmPassword" type="password" class="form-control" name="ConfirmPassword" required>
                                                                    <label> @Resource.Password</label>
                                                                    <div class="icon-bg text-center">
                                                                        <i class="fas fa-lock-alt"></i>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                            </div>
                                        </div>





                                        <div class="agreec">
                                            <input class="inp-cbx" id="cbx" type="checkbox" style="display: none;" />
                                            <label class="cbx" for="cbx">
                                                <span>
                                                    <svg width="12px" height="9px" viewbox="0 0 12 9">
                                                        <polyline points="1 5 4 8 11 1"></polyline>
                                                    </svg>
                                                </span><span>
                                                    &nbsp;
                                                    @*أوافق على كافة*@
                                                @Resource.IagreeToAll

                                                    <a href="/pages/details/4" class="conditions-link" target="_blank"> @Resource.TermsandConditions </a>
                                                </span>
                                            </label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="actions">
                                    <div class="thank-text">
                                        <p>@ViewBag.Result</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li><a href="/account/register"><span class="js-btn-prev" title="BACK"> @Resource.Previous</span></a></li>

                                        <li><button name="submit"><span class="js-btn-next " title="NEXT"> @Resource.Register  </span></button></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bottom-vector position-absolute">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- step 2 -->
                        <div class="multisteps-form__panel" data-animation="scaleIn">
                            <div class="wizard-forms form-step-3">
                                <span class="step-no position-absolute">  @Resource.Step3</span>
                                <div class="wizard-progress">
                                    <span>  @Resource.Stage3of3</span>
                                    <div class="progress">
                                        <div class="progress-bar" style="width: 100%;">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="wizard-inner-box">
                                    <div class="thank-content text-center">
                                        <div class="thank-img">
                                            <img src="/Content/front/assets/img/th1.png" alt="">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="thank-text">
                                            <h2> @Resource.ThankYouforregisteringInthesite </h2>
                                            <p>@Resource.YourAccounthasbeensuccessfullyregisteredPleasecheckyouremailtoactivateyouraccount</p>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="thank-btn text-uppercase">
                                            <a href="/home/">  @Resource.BackToHome</a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- step 3 -->
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

}


<style>
    .select2-dropdown {
        margin-top: 0px !important;
    }
</style>
